    <div class="rejuve-joints__content" id="rejuve-joints-container">
        <div class="rejuve-joints__info-left rejuve-joints__info-textbox" id="rejuve-joints-textbox-left">
            <div class="rejuve-joints__line rejuve-joints__line--left" id="left-line"></div>
            <img src="{{ 'rejuve-joint.png'| asset_url}}" alt="Joint" class="rejuve-joints__info-image-mobile" width="200" height="200">
            <h3 class="rejuve-joints__info-title"><em>Regenerating Synovial Fluid for Joint Lubrication</em> (via
                BioHyaluronic™)</h3>
            <div class="rejuve-joints__writeup">
                <p>
                    Our knees, hips, wrists, shoulders, elbows (and many other joints) depend on healthy synovial fluid
                    to lubricate the joint capsules and minimize friction. Healthy synovial fluid is composed almost
                    entirely of a remarkably low-friction complex of Hyaluronic Acid bound to phospholipids.
                </p>
                <p>
                    As we age, our synovial fluid degrades, leading to joint stiffness and pain. Reversing this process
                    is the key to restoring joint smoothness, flexibility and comfort.
                </p>
                <p>
                    With Re·juve, we developed BioHyaluronic™, a breakthrough complex of Hyaluronic Acid and
                    phospholipids that rebuilds synovial fluid in the joint. (more on BioHyaluronic™ in the ingredients
                    section below)
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <img src="{{ 'rejuve-joint.png'| asset_url}}" alt="Joint" class="rejuve-joints__central-image" width="242" height="242" id="rejuve-central-image">
