            <div class="rejuve-joints__line rejuve-joints__line--right" id="right-line"></div>
            <img src="{{ 'rejuve-joint.png'| asset_url}}" alt="Joint" class="rejuve-joints__info-image-mobile" width="200" height="200">
            <h3 class="rejuve-joints__info-title"><em>Protecting + Regenerating Cartilage</em> (via Liposomal Glutathione +
                Aronia Extract)</h3>
            <div class="rejuve-joints__writeup">
                <p>
                    Cartilage sits on the contact surfaces of our bones, functioning as cushioning for our joints. As we
                    age, our cartilage is subjected to oxidative degeneration, breaking down the cartilage and rendering
                    it less effective. The result is friction, pain and inflammation in the joint.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Re·juve uses two strategies to protect cartilage from oxidative degeneration and stimulate
                    regeneration: Liposomal Glutathione and Aronia Extract (see why below).
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
